data.description: A really cute home. The kitchen has been recently remodeled. With soft closing drawers and cabinets, pull out shelves in the cabinets, new counter, new sink, new tile floors. The living room has new laminate floors throughout, big beautiful windows allowing a lot of natural light, with beautiful views. The main floor bathroom was just remodeled. The seller is currently putting new flooring on the stairs and is currently remodeling the master bathroom on the second level. The solar will be paid off by the seller at close of escrow. The electrical panel has a plug to connect a generator to the home. No garage but the carport is new. The front deck is new.
